To install the PlusCalc library and interpreter run the following commands:

$ make
$ sudo make install

To remove object files as well as built libraries and programs, run:

$ make clean

To uninstall the PlusCalc library and interpreter, run:

$ sudo make uninstall

During the installation process, the makefile copies libpluscalc.a to /usr/lib, pluscalc.h to /usr/include and pluscalcint to /usr/bin. Change this as needed.
